  // Certificate Gallery Callout
  section.container(style="margin: 60px auto;")
    .cert-callout(style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, white, #fff1eb); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);")
      div(style="max-width: 500px;")
        h2(style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text-dark);") Showcase Your Skills
        p(style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;") Did you know you can earn verifiable credentials? Unlock expert certificates for completing complex skill paths and share them directly to your LinkedIn.
        a.btn.btn-primary(href="/certificates") View Certificate Gallery
      div(style="position: relative; width: 200px; height: 140px; border-radius: 12px; background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589330694653-efa64753baaa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80') center/cover; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: rotate(5deg);")
        .ribbon(style="position: absolute; top: -10px; right: -10px; background: var(--primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px;")
          i.fas.fa-award

  // Features grid
  section(style="background-color: #f3ede4; padding: 80px 0;")
    .container(style="text-align: center;")
      h2(style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 16px;") Why Learn on SkillStreak?
      p(style="color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px;") We've combined the dopamine of gaming with the rigor of higher education to help you achieve more in less time.
      
      .features-grid(style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px;")
        .feature-card(style="background: white; padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);")
          .icon(style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: #ffe4d6; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 24px;")
            i.fas.fa-gamepad
          h3(style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;") Gamified Learning
          p(style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px;") Earn XP, unlock badges, and climb the leaderboards as you master new concepts.
        
        .feature-card(style="background: white; padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);")
          .icon(style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: #ffe4d6; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 24px;")
            i.fas.fa-users
          h3(style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;") Community Support
          p(style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px;") Join thousands of learners to solve problems, share tips, and collaborate on projects.
          
        .feature-card(style="background: white; padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);")
          .icon(style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: #ffe4d6; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 24px;")
            i.fas.fa-chalkboard-teacher
          h3(style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;") Mentor Access
          p(style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px;") Get 1-on-1 feedback from industry professionals who are currently working at top firms.
          
        .feature-card(style="background: white; padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);")
          .icon(style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: #ffe4d6; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 24px;")
            i.fas.fa-briefcase
          h3(style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;") Job Opportunities
          p(style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px;") Our partner network looks specifically for top-ranking SkillStreak learners for new roles.
